com.facebook.buck.cxx

Class MungingDebugPathSanitizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.cxx.DebugPathSanitizer
      • com.facebook.buck.cxx.MungingDebugPathSanitizer

  • public class MungingDebugPathSanitizer
extends DebugPathSanitizer
    This sanitizer works by munging the compiler output to replace paths. Currently, this just supports sanitizing the compilation directory that compilers typically embed in binaries when including debug sections (e.g. using "-g" with gcc/clang inserts the compilation directory in the DW_AT_comp_dir DWARF field).
